ke a clockwork dragon.</span></div> 		<div id="personalbio"><span class="title">Personal Bio ::</span> <span class="value">     A smidgeon of a thing I was born, even for a Gnome.  Being the smallest of my bunch, I was always cast aside for the stronger and taller gnome children.  How I envied them, so proud of their stature and bearing.  
     My mind was sharp though, more so than most.  Lacking the physical prowess of my peers, I entertained myself with the world around me.  Exploring and discovery were the joys of my youth.  I would often steal away to look at the great King Ak’anon and the majesty of his court.  Many a night I lay there dreaming I was one of his knights doing glorious things and making my people proud.
     Years past, and I was still a wee lad.  My envy built and soon turned into loathing.  “Why?” I muttered, “Why work so hard your entire life to have it all taken away when you will just die?”  The king knew this, for he has seen his court change throughout the years.  He himself of course can not die, being clockwork, but his followers can.   Including myself.  This revelation disturbed me greatly.
     Down in the Mines of Malfunction I found my answer.  The dark ones new of death, and how to manipulate it.  “I would be ready…” I exclaimed.  When the death came for me, I would be it’s master.  It matters not how strong and tall these other Gnomes are, I would be stronger yet.  I would survive where they have perished.  All these years of  being cast aside tempered me into what I am now becoming.  A necromancer, and I am good at what I now do.
</span></div>	</div> 	<div id="contactinfo">		<h2>My Contact Information</h2>		<div id="email"><span class="title">Email Address ::</span>  <span class="privatevalue">private</span></div>		<div id="pm">		<span class="title">My Inbox ::</span> 						<span class="value"><a href="" title="Send a message using the ezboard inbox feature" >Send me a Message!</a></span>				</div>		<div id="im"><span class="title">IM ::</span> <span class="value">None - </span></div>		<div id="link"><span class="title">Personal Link ::</span> <span class="value"><a href="" target="_blank">My Personal Link</a></span></div>		<div id="recentposts"><span class="title">Recent Posts ::</span> 										<span class="value">		<dl>				<dt><a href="http://pub64.ezboard.com/fminionsofnightmarefrm7.showMessage?topicID=200.topic" title="post" target="_blank">Regarding Naywyn's IRL Pregnancy.</a></dt>		<dd><em>from <a href="http://pub64.ezboard.com/fminionsofnightmarefrm7" title="forum the above post is in" target="_blank">Visitor Forum</a></em></dd>				<dt><a href="http://pub219.ezboard.com/fnecropolisfrm8.showMessage?topicID=39.topic" title="post" target="_blank">Regarding Naywyn's IRL pregnancy.</a></dt>		<dd><em>from <a href="http://pub219.ezboard.com/fnecropolisfrm8" title="forum the above post is in" target="_blank">(Out of Character IRL Forum)</a></em></dd>				<dt><a href="http://pub72.ezboard.com/fcastlebloodlustfrm9.showMessage?topicID=153.topic" title="post" target="_blank">Regarding Naywyn's IRL pregnancy.</a></dt>		<dd><em>from <a href="http://pub72.ezboard.com/fcastlebloodlustfrm9" title="forum the above post is in" target="_blank">Greater Commons</a></em></dd>				<dt><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm62.showMessage?topicID=618.topic" title="post" target="_blank">Regarding Naywyn's IRL pregnancy.</a></dt>		<dd><em>from <a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm62" title="forum the above post is in" target="